videos.description: UConn coach Geno Auriemma breaks down the No. 1 Huskies' 66-54 win over the No. 2 ranked South Carolina Gamecocks and how a game like this builds confidence for tournament time.
videos.headline: Geno: We handled this challenge like every other one

videos.description: Breanna Stewart breaks down her 25-point, 10-rebound performance for UConn in a 66-54 win over South Carolina.
videos.headline: Stewart comes up big for Huskies

videos.description: Dave O'Brien and Doris Burke break down Connecticut's victory over South Carolina.
videos.headline: Connecticut's leaders step up over South Carolina
